==English==
===Etymology===
From Greek [[πλουτοκρατια]], from [[πλουτος]] ‘wealth’ + [[κράτος]] ‘power, might’.

===Noun===
'''plutocracy'''
# [[government]] by the [[wealthy]]
# a controlling class of the [[wealthy]]

